fulltitle: Towards a Revolutionary Constitution: Black Panthers Michael Tabor and Huey P. Newton (1970)
title: Towards a Revolutionary Constitution: Black Panthers Michael Tabor and Huey P. Newton (1970)
_filename: _Towards a Revolutionary Constitution - Black Panthers Michael Tabor and Huey P. Newton (1970).mp4
description:
Keynote address by Michael Tabor and speech by Huey Newton on the political objectives of the Black Panthers.

Reported by Bruce Soloway.

PRA Archive #: BB3847.01
Date Recorded on: in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, 4-6 Sept. 1970.
Date Broadcast on: WBAI, 15 Sept. 1970.
Item duration: 2 reels (104 min.) : 7 1/2 ips, mono.
